page.title: 11PERSONALITIES IN RINGSTEAD
page.content: Many inhabitants have retired from responsible positions in the Armed Forces Commerce and Banking. {THE REVD.DR. WILLIAM JACOB}is the Selection Secretary to the Advisory Council for the Church's Ministry,of the Church of England General Synod. {LORD MELCHETT}is a former Minister of State for Northern Ireland who now devotes his time to farming and the Conservation of Nnatural Beauty,etc. {RAY.J.EDDINGTON}has the Old Rectory as his English holiday home.He is Chairman of Weston Food Distributors,a giant consortium in Canada,and is known as "The Mr. Sainsbury of Canada"
